sequenceDiagram
    actor "Mobile Client" as MobileClient
    participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
    participant "Service Request Service" as ServiceRequestService
    participant "Persistence Layer" as PersistenceLayer
    participant "Messaging Infrastructure" as MessagingInfrastructure
    participant "Notification Service" as NotificationService
    participant "Audit Service" as AuditService

    activate APIGateway
    MobileClient->>APIGateway: 1. 1. Dispute Service Request
    APIGateway-->>MobileClient: 8. HTTP 200 OK
    activate ServiceRequestService
    APIGateway->>ServiceRequestService: 2. 2. Forward Dispute Request
    ServiceRequestService-->>APIGateway: 7. HTTP 200 OK
    activate NotificationService
    MessagingInfrastructure->>NotificationService: 9. 9. Consume ServiceRequestStatusChanged Event
    NotificationService->>NotificationService: 10. 10. Prepare and Send Push Notification
    activate AuditService
    MessagingInfrastructure->>AuditService: 11. 11. Consume CriticalActionOccurred Event
    AuditService->>PersistenceLayer: 12. 12. Persist Audit Log

    note over ServiceRequestService: Business Rule Enforcement: The core business logic for the 7-day dispute window (REQ-FUNC-008) is...
    note over MessagingInfrastructure: Decoupled Communication: Notifications and auditing are handled asynchronously via an event-drive...

    deactivate AuditService
    deactivate NotificationService
    deactivate ServiceRequestService
    deactivate APIGateway
